            <li><strong>Wheel bearings</strong> - No play, rotate smoothly without noise</li>
            <li><strong>Tighten wheel nuts</strong> - Should be properly torqued</li>
            <li><strong>Check for wheel misalignment</strong> - Uneven tire wear indicates problem</li>
          </ul>

